8.02	Salil_Chowdhury	Salil Chowdhury	Salil Chowdhury (Bengali: , Hindi: , Malayalam: ) was an Indian music composer, who mainly composed for Bengali, Hindi, and Malayalam films. He was also a poet and a playwright. He is affectionately called Salilda by his admirers.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6e/SalilChowdhury1002.jpg/220px-SalilChowdhury1002.jpg
